      "body" : "tACK https://github.com/vostrnad/bitcoin/commit/8c1114aa61c46e58efb44368b5428d3ccb65f9d0\r\n\r\nSteps to test:\r\n\r\n1. Build [vostrnad branch](https://github.com/vostrnad/bitcoin/tree/permitbarepubkey)\r\n1. Start a regtest with `-chain=regtest`\r\n1. Create a wallet with `bitcoin-cli createwallet`\r\n1. Get address with `bitcoin-cli getnewaddress`\r\n1. Generate blocks to get bitcoins `generatetoaddress 500 <address obtained previously>`\r\n1. Create a P2PK tx, this [repository](https://github.com/dianerey/bech32p2pkaddress) can be useful to you.\r\n1. Test if the tx is accepted with `bitcoin-cli testmempoolaccept '[\"<RAW tx>\"]'`\r\n\r\nResult obtained in my case with `-permitbarepubkey=0`:\r\n\r\n```\r\n[\r\n  {\r\n    \"txid\": \"03c1140befa500e1809f5fa6950a45516f651a2e88fe252ac6c9fec393c68f11\",\r\n    \"wtxid\": \"03c1140befa500e1809f5fa6950a45516f651a2e88fe252ac6c9fec393c68f11\",\r\n    \"allowed\": false,\r\n    \"reject-reason\": \"bare-pubkey\"\r\n  }\r\n]\r\n```",
